<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to {{companyName}}</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border: 1px solid #dddddd;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #f8f8f8;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #dddddd;
        }
        .logo {
            max-width: 150px;
            height: auto;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #28a745;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #f8f8f8;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666666;
            border-top: 1px solid #dddddd;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dzivbyc4z/image/upload/v1737740103/favicon_zxnv9v.ico" alt="{{companyName}} Logo" class="logo">
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h1>Welcome to {{companyName}}!</h1>
            <p>Dear {{name}},</p>
            <p>We're thrilled to have you on board. Thank you for joining our community!</p>
            <p>Here are a few things you can do to get started:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Use free credits</li>
                <li>Explore our features</li>
                <li>Tell your friends</li>
            </ul>
            <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, our support team is always here to help.</p>
            <p>
                <a href="{{dashboardLink}}" class="button">Go to Your Dashboard</a>
            </p>
            <p>We're excited to see what you'll accomplish with {{companyName}}!</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Best regards,<br>The {{companyName}} Team</p>
            <p>&copy; {{currentYear}} {{companyName}}. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>

